<p>The Creative Commons Clinic (ccClinic) is a research and education project funded by the <a href="http://www.cci.edu.au">ARC Centre of Excellence for Creative Industries &amp; Innovation</a>, which<br />
engages with Creative Commons to research and promote its implementation in Australia. </p>
