<h4 class="meta">
<a href="http://techblog.creativecommons.org" title="TechBlog">CC Techblog</a>, July 24, 2007 10:44 PM                    &nbsp;<span style="font-weight: normal; font-size: x-small; color:#000000;">(Licensed under <a about="http://techblog.creativecommons.org/2007/07/24/cc-openoffice-addin-update-added-impress-funcionality/" rel="license" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/" title="License information" style="font-size: x-small;">Attribution 3.0 Unported</a>)</span>
